description:
The Lob API (formerly Infraprint) is a printing API organized around REST. Our API is designed to have predictable, resource-oriented URLs and uses HTTP response codes to indicate any API errors. To send a print job you need to:

Create an address
Create an object - an object is the content you will be printing
Once you have done this you can send this a job to the printer!
